\u4e08.kakimashou_def: length, ten shaku, measure, Mr., Ms., height, stature, all (one has), only, that's all, merely

Kun'yomi: たけ height ② length (esp. of clothing) ③ all (one has) ④ magnificence (of a waka poem, etc.)
だけ only ② as much as
On'yomi: ジョウ 3.03 meters (ten shaku) ② length ③ Mr.

Kun'yomi: みだれる to be disordered ② to be discomposed ③ to lapse into chaos (due to war, etc.)
みだす to throw into disorder
あらそう to compete ② to quarrel ③ to deny (e.g. evidence)
ほとけ Buddha ② Buddhist image ③ the dead ④ merciful person

On'yomi: レイ command ② nth year in the Reiwa era (May 1, 2019-)
Nanori: りょう administrative and civil code

\u4f1d.kakimashou_def: transmit, go along, walk along, follow, report, communicate, legend, tradition

Kun'yomi: つたわる to spread (of a rumor, news, etc.) ② to be handed down (from generation to generation) ③ to be introduced (to a country, region, etc.) ④ to be conveyed (of a feeling, impression, etc.)
つて means of making contact ② connections
On'yomi: デン legend ② biography ③ method ④ horseback transportation and communication relay system used in ancient Japan

\u4f4d.kakimashou_def: rank, grade, throne, crown, about, some

Kun'yomi: くらい throne ② government position ③ social standing ④ grade (of quality, etc.)
On'yomi: イ rank ② decimal place ③ counter for ghosts

Kun'yomi: ひくい low (rank, degree, value, content, quality, etc.) ② low (position) ③ short (height) ④ deep (voice)
On'yomi: テイ low (level, value, price, etc.)

\u4f59.kakimashou_def: too much, myself, surplus, other, remainder, I, my, me, surname

Kun'yomi: あまり remainder ② (not) very ③ extreme ④ more than
あんまり remainder ② (not) very ③ extreme ④ more than
On'yomi: ヨ other ② over ③ I

Kun'yomi: たとえる to compare (something) to
On'yomi: レイ example ② precedent ③ custom

\u4fbf.kakimashou_def: convenience, facility, excrement, feces, letter, chance

On'yomi: ベン convenience ② excreta (esp. feces)
ビン flight (e.g. airline flight) ② mail ③ opportunity

\u4fc2.kakimashou_def: person in charge, connection, duty, concern oneself

Kun'yomi: かかる to be the work of ② to concern
かかわる to be affected ② to be concerned with ③ to stick to (opinions)

On'yomi: シン honesty ② trust ③ counter for received messages
